<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to ITAN!</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      .header {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #e8f4f8;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .content h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #dc3545;
      }
      .content p {
        margin: 15px 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #dc3545;
        color: #fff !important;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #888;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        background-color: #fafafa;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to ITAN, Reader!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= @reader.first_name || 'there' %> 👋</h2>
        <p>Thank you for joining <strong>ITAN Global Publishing</strong> — the home of African stories.</p>
        <p>You're now part of a growing community of readers who believe in the power of local storytelling and support African authors.</p>
        <p>As a reader on ITAN, you can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Discover and enjoy powerful African literature</li>
          <li>Support authors directly through your purchases</li>
          <li>Get secure access to your books anytime, anywhere</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We’re thrilled to have you on board!</p>
        <a href="<%= @frontend_url %>/reader/sign_in" class="cta-button">Start Reading</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        If you need help, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@itan.app">support@itan.app</a><br>
        Visit ITAN: <%= @frontend_url %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
